            <title>[LU-11409] only first 100 OSC can shrink grants</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11409</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;the logic in&#160;osc_grant_work_handler() wants to limit number of shrink requests in flight,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;but it doesn&apos;t take skipped OSCs into account, meaning only the first 100 OSCs are subject to this procedure.&lt;/p&gt;

